caption.title: Weekly estimates of key model parameters: Infectious period for A(H1N1) (A), A(H3N2) (B), and B (C); immunity period for A(H1N1) (D), A(H3N2) (E), and B (F); and strength of cross-immunity for the six virus-pairs (G-L).
caption.p: Solid lines and surrounding areas show the posterior mean and 95% CI estimates and dashed lines show the prior ranges.
